{"type":"message","id":"b4778751","parentId":"3288043d","timestamp":"2026-04-11T12:32:39.857Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Saturday, April 11th, 2026 - 8:32 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-11 12:32 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775910759847}}
{"type":"message","id":"2d4786e7","parentId":"b4778751","timestamp":"2026-04-11T12:32:46.850Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is starting a new session. According to the instructions, I should run my Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding. Let me check what I need to do.\n\nLooking at the instructions:\n1. Run Session Startup sequence - read required files before responding\n2. Greet the user in configured persona\n3. Keep it 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do\n4. If runtime model differs from default_model, mention the default model\n5. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning\n\nI notice there's a \"Session Startup sequence\" mentioned. Looking at my project context files:\n- MEMORY.md mentions \"每次会话启动必须读取 MEMORY.md\" (Must read MEMORY.md at session startup)\n\nSo I should read MEMORY.md at minimum. Let me also check if there are any other required files.\n\nFrom MEMORY.md I can see:\n- It's the entry point for the long-term memory system\n- Contains references to other memory files\n\nLet me read MEMORY.md first, then greet the user.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dad1515b040a4de7a300bf2c","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":19217,"output":255,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19472,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775910759863,"responseId":"chatcmpl-9bd8b283-5270-4716-ad9b-dc4828551b79"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e9fc4aca","parentId":"2d4786e7","timestamp":"2026-04-11T12:32:46.921Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_dad1515b040a4de7a300bf2c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nversion: 1.0\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\nmaintainer: ai\nttl_days: 90\n---\n\n# MEMORY.md - 核心长期记忆库\n\n> 本文件是 OpenClaw 长期记忆系统的入口，每次会话自动加载。\n\n## 📁 模块索引\n\n- [个人偏好](memory/preferences.md)\n- [项目: OpenClaw](memory/projects/openclaw.md)\n- [固化知识](memory/knowledge.md)\n- [临时记忆](memory/ephemeral/)（自动清理）\n- [实体页](memory/entities/) — 核心 25 个\n\n## 🧠 实体页 (核心 25)\n\n> 精简后核心页面，按需使用\n\n### 系统基础\n\n| 页面 | 描述 |\n|------|------|\n| [OpenClaw](memory/entities/openclaw.md) | 主项目、架构、组件 |\n| [Skills](memory/entities/skills.md) | 已安装技能清单 |\n| [Memory](memory/entities/memory.md) | 记忆系统本身 |\n| [Model](memory/entities/model.md) | 模型配置 |\n| [User](memory/entities/user.md) | 用户档案 |\n| [Preferences](memory/entities/preferences.md) | 用户偏好 |\n\n### LLM Wiki 核心\n\n| 页面 | 描述 |\n|------|------|\n| [LLM Wiki](memory/entities/llm-wiki.md) | LLM Wiki 模式概念 |\n| [Ingest](memory/entities/ingest.md) | 知识摄取流程 |\n| [Query Workflow](memory/entities/query-workflow.md) | 问答与写回 |\n| [Lint](memory/entities/lint.md) | 健康检查 |\n| [Log](memory/entities/log.md) | 时间线记录 |\n| [Raw Sources](memory/entities/raw-sources.md) | 原始文档库 |\n\n### 关键工具\n\n| 页面 | 描述 |\n|------|------|\n| [Obsidian](memory/entities/obsidian.md) | 推荐 IDE |\n| [Search](memory/entities/search.md) | 搜索工具 |\n| [Git](memory/entities/git.md) | 版本控制 |\n| [Backup Strategy](memory/entities/backup-strategy.md) | 备份恢复 |\n\n### 规范与快速入口\n\n| 页面 | 描述 |\n|------|------|\n| [Wiki Schema](memory/entities/wiki-schema.md) | 页面规范 |\n| [Quick Start](memory/entities/quick-start.md) | 快速入门 |\n| [Wiki Prompts](memory/entities/wiki-prompts.md) | 用户指令 |\n| [System Integration](memory/entities/system-integration.md) | 系统整合 |\n| [Contradictions](memory/entities/contradictions.md) | 矛盾管理 |\n\n### 自我改进\n\n| 页面 | 描述 |\n|------|------|\n| [Self-Improving](memory/entities/self-improving.md) | 自我改进系统 |\n| [Corrections](memory/entities/corrections.md) | 错误记录 |\n| [AI Usage](memory/entities/ai-usage.md) | AI 如何使用 Wiki |\n| [AI Research](memory/entities/ai-research.md) | AI 研究 |\n\n---\n\n## 🛠️ 关于小六 (AI)\n\n- **事实** [事实] 小六是 OpenClaw AI 助手\n- **规则** [规则] 每次会话启动必须读取 MEMORY.md\n- **规则** [规则] 学到新东西立即写入 ~/self-improving/\n\n## ⚙️ 核心规则\n\n- **规则** [规则] 对话里说过的话 = 忘记；写进文件的内容 = 永远记得\n- **规则** [规则] 每次纠正立即写入 ~/self-improving/corrections.md\n- **规则** [规则] 绝不说谎（不知道就说不知道）\n- **规则** [规则] 回答代码时优先提供 Python 示例\n- **路径** [路径] 工作区 `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace`\n- **路径** [路径] 自我改进 `~/self-improving/`\n\n---\n\n## 📚 归档内容\n\n不常用的页面已移至 `entities-archive/`，需要时可以从归档恢复。\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*\n*使用 openclaw memory search \"关键词\" 验证索引*"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775910766909}}
{"type":"message","id":"7b02cd82","parentId":"e9fc4aca","timestamp":"2026-04-11T12:32:49.900Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I've read MEMORY.md. Key points:\n- I'm \"小六\" (Xiao Liu) - the OpenClaw AI assistant\n- Default model is volcengine-plan/doubao-seed-2.0-pro\n- Runtime model is codingplan/minimax-m2.5 (differs from default)\n- Rules: remember written things, record corrections, don't lie, prefer Python examples\n\nLet me greet the user now. The runtime model (codingplan/minimax-m2.5) differs from default_model (volcengine-plan/doubao-seed-2.0-pro), so I should mention that.\n\nI should be myself - use my defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. The persona seems to be \"小六\" - a helpful AI assistant. Keep it 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n我是小六，你的 OpenClaw AI 助手。当前默认模型是 doubao-seed-2.0-pro。\n\n有什么我可以帮你的？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":20406,"output":203,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20609,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775910766921,"responseId":"chatcmpl-af578033-60a6-4c95-9edf-88039362ba45"}}
