{"type":"message","id":"5b35d1f3","parentId":"e52fd454","timestamp":"2026-04-11T12:38:33.055Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a heartbeat poll. According to my instructions, I need to check if there's anything that needs attention.\n\nLooking at the context:\n1. The user sent me a technical document about multi-model routing\n2. I provided analysis and asked follow-up questions\n3. There's no active task running\n4. There's nothing in HEARTBEAT.md that indicates any pending work\n\nThe last user message was my question asking if they want to start Phase 1 or discuss Phase 1.5. The user hasn't responded yet. There's no indication of any ongoing task that needs attention.\n\nSince nothing needs attention, I should reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nHEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":21524,"output":139,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21663,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775911109891,"responseId":"chatcmpl-cc705170-31a6-40a3-abe7-09a258378efb"}}
{"type":"message","id":"df6d6939","parentId":"5b35d1f3","timestamp":"2026-04-11T12:39:53.076Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-04-11 20:39 GMT+8] 学习一下，给出预案并思考，先回答我不用操作：你的分析非常精准，“外挂式优先”确实是最适合当前阶段的路径。以下直接给出 Phase 1 和 Phase 1.5 的具体实施方案，你可以立即开始落地。\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1：配置落地与校验脚本（30分钟内完成）\n\n### 1.1 创建目录和配置文件\n\n```bash\nmkdir -p ~/.openclaw/config\n```\n\n**`~/.openclaw/config/models.json`**\n```json\n{\n \"version\": \"1.0\",\n \"providers\": {\n \"minimax\": {\n \"type\": \"openai-compatible\",\n \"baseUrl\": \"https://api.minimax.chat/v1\",\n \"apiKey\": \"${MINIMAX_API_KEY}\"\n },\n \"deepseek\": {\n \"type\": \"openai-compatible\",\n \"baseUrl\": \"https://api.deepseek.com/v1\",\n \"apiKey\": \"${DEEPSEEK_API_KEY}\"\n }\n },\n \"models\": {\n \"fast\": {\n \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n \"modelId\": \"minimax-m2.5\",\n \"fallback\": \"deep\",\n \"timeout\": 30000,\n \"maxRetries\": 2\n },\n \"deep\": {\n \"provider\": \"deepseek\",\n \"modelId\": \"deepseek-chat\",\n \"fallback\": \"fast\",\n \"timeout\": 60000,\n \"maxRetries\": 1\n }\n }\n}\n```\n\n**`~/.openclaw/config/routing_rules.json`**\n```json\n{\n \"version\": \"1.0\",\n \"rules\": [\n {\n \"id\": \"code_keywords\",\n \"priority\": 100,\n \"condition\": { \"contains\": [\"写代码\", \"编程\", \"重构\", \"debug\", \"脚本\", \"部署\", \"优化\", \"修复\", \"实现\"] },\n \"target_agent\": \"fast_agent\"\n },\n {\n \"id\": \"deep_keywords\",\n \"priority\": 100,\n \"condition\": { \"contains\": [\"分析\", \"推理\", \"数学\", \"证明\", \"论文\", \"原理\"] },\n \"target_agent\": \"deep_agent\"\n },\n {\n \"id\": \"classifier_task\",\n \"priority\": 80,\n \"condition\": { \"classifier_label\": [\"task_multi_step\", \"high_risk_automated\", \"fault_recovery\"] },\n \"target_agent\": \"fast_agent\"\n },\n {\n \"id\": \"classifier_reasoning\",\n \"priority\": 80,\n \"condition\": { \"classifier_label\": [\"expert_user\", \"vague_request\"] },\n \"target_agent\": \"deep_agent\"\n },\n {\n \"id\": \"fallback\",\n \"priority\": 0,\n \"condition\": { \"always\": true },\n \"target_agent\": \"fast_agent\"\n }\n ]\n}\n```\n\n### 1.2 更新 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` 中的 Agent 定义\n\n```json\n{\n \"agents\": {\n \"list\": [\n {\n \"id\": \"fast_agent\",\n \"name\": \"Fast Agent\",\n \"workspace\": \"/home/ai/.openclaw/agents/fast\",\n \"modelRef\": \"fast\"\n },\n {\n \"id\": \"deep_agent\",\n \"name\": \"Deep Agent\",\n \"workspace\": \"/home/ai/.openclaw/agents/deep\",\n \"modelRef\": \"deep\"\n }\n ],\n \"defaults\": { \"modelRef\": \"fast\" }\n }\n}\n```\n\n### 1.3 配置校验脚本\n\n**`~/.openclaw/scripts/validate-config.js`**\n```javascript\n#!/usr/bin/env node\nconst fs = require('fs');\nconst path = require('path');\n\nconst configDir = path.join(process.env.HOME, '.openclaw/config');\nconst modelsPath = path.join(configDir, 'models.json');\nconst rulesPath = path.join(configDir, 'routing_rules.json');\nconst openclawPath = path.join(process.env.HOME, '.openclaw/openclaw.json');\n\nlet hasError = false;\n\n// 1. 检查文件存在\n[modelsPath, rulesPath, openclawPath].forEach(f => {\n if (!fs.existsSync(f)) {\n console.error(`❌ Missing: ${f}`);\n hasError = true;\n }\n});\nif (hasError) process.exit(1);\n\nconst models = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(modelsPath));\nconst rules = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(rulesPath));\nconst openclaw = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(openclawPath));\n\n// 2. 校验 provider 环境变量\nObject.entries(models.providers).forEach(([name, cfg]) => {\n const envKey = cfg.apiKey.replace('${', '').replace('}', '');\n if (!process.env[envKey]) {\n console.warn(`⚠️ Environment variable ${envKey} not set (provider: ${name})`);\n }\n});\n\n// 3. 校验 modelRef 存在\nconst agentList = openclaw.agents?.list || [];\nconst modelIds = Object.keys(models.models);\nagentList.forEach(agent => {\n if (agent.modelRef && !modelIds.includes(agent.modelRef)) {\n console.error(`❌ Agent '${agent.id}' references unknown modelRef '${agent.modelRef}'`);\n hasError = true;\n }\n});\n\n// 4. 校验 target_agent 存在\nconst agentIds = agentList.map(a => a.id);\nrules.rules.forEach(rule => {\n if (!agentIds.includes(rule.target_agent)) {\n console.error(`❌ Rule '${rule.id}' targets unknown agent '${rule.target_agent}'`);\n hasError = true;\n }\n});\n\n// 5. 校验 fallback 模型存在\nObject.entries(models.models).forEach(([name, cfg]) => {\n if (cfg.fallback && !models.models[cfg.fallback]) {\n console.error(`❌ Model '${name}' fallback '${cfg.fallback}' not found`);\n hasError = true;\n }\n});\n\n// 6. 警告：priority 重复\nconst priorities = rules.rules.map(r => r.priority);\nif (new Set(priorities).size !== priorities.length) {\n console.warn('⚠️ Duplicate priority values detected in routing rules');\n}\n\nconsole.log(hasError ? '❌ Validation failed' : '✅ Validation passed');\nprocess.exit(hasError ? 1 : 0);\n```\n\n```bash\nchmod +x ~/.openclaw/scripts/validate-config.js\n```\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1.5：外挂式 Router 设计（在 3102 代理中实现）\n\n### 设计原则\n- **不修改 Gateway 源码**，在现有 `~/.openclaw/proxy/index.js` 中扩展路由逻辑。\n- **复用已有的分类器客户端**（`v8Client.js`）。\n- **最小化延迟**：关键词匹配在本地完成，仅必要时调用分类器。\n\n### 具体实现位置\n\n在 `~/.openclaw/proxy/index.js` 的 `app.post('/api/chat/send', ...)` 内部，**在调用分类器之前**插入路由决策。\n\n### 核心代码片段\n\n```javascript\n// 1. 加载配置（启动时加载一次，全局缓存）\nconst modelsConfig = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('/home/ai/.openclaw/config/models.json'));\nconst rulesConfig = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('/home/ai/.openclaw/config/routing_rules.json'));\nconst openclawConfig = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('/home/ai/.openclaw/openclaw.json'));\n\n// 2. 路由决策函数\nfunction routeAgent(userMessage, classifierResult) {\n const rules = [...rulesConfig.rules].sort((a, b) => b.priority - a.priority);\n \n for (const rule of rules) {\n if (rule.condition.always) continue; // fallback 最后处理\n \n if (rule.condition.contains) {\n const matched = rule.condition.contains.some(kw => userMessage.includes(kw));\n if (matched) return rule.target_agent;\n }\n \n if (rule.condition.classifier_label && classifierResult) {\n const matched = rule.condition.classifier_label.includes(classifierResult.scene);\n if (matched) return rule.target_agent;\n }\n }\n \n // 默认 fallback\n const fallback = rules.find(r => r.condition.always);\n return fallback ? fallback.target_agent : 'fast_agent';\n}\n\n// 3. 在消息处理中使用\napp.post('/api/chat/send', async (req, res) => {\n const userMessage = req.body.message;\n \n // 分类器调用（可带缓存）\n let classifierResult = null;\n try {\n classifierResult = await classify(userMessage);\n } catch (e) {\n console.warn('Classifier unavailable, routing by keywords only');\n }\n \n const targetAgentId = routeAgent(userMessage, classifierResult);\n \n // 查找 Agent 配置，获取 modelRef\n const agent = openclawConfig.agents.list.find(a => a.id === targetAgentId);\n const modelRef = agent?.modelRef || 'fast';\n const modelConfig = modelsConfig.models[modelRef];\n \n console.log(`Routing: \"${userMessage.substring(0,30)}\" -> ${targetAgentId} (${modelConfig.provider}/${modelConfig.modelId})`);\n \n // 后续：使用 modelConfig 调用对应 LLM API\n // ...\n});\n```\n\n### 分类器降级与缓存\n\n```javascript\nconst NodeCache = require('node-cache');\nconst classifyCache = new NodeCache({ stdTTL: 300 }); // 5分钟\n\nasync function getClassifierResult(message) {\n let result = classifyCache.get(message);\n if (result) return result;\n \n try {\n result = await classify(message);\n classifyCache.set(message, result);\n return result;\n } catch (e) {\n return null; // 降级\n }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 下一步\n\n1. **执行 Phase 1**：创建上述配置文件，运行校验脚本确认通过。\n2. **修改 3102 代理**：按 Phase 1.5 设计在 `index.js` 中加入路由逻辑。\n3. **重启代理**：`systemctl --user restart openclaw-proxy`\n4. **测试验证**：发送编程类、推理类、闲聊类消息，观察代理日志中的路由决策。\n\n需要我把 Phase 1.5 的完整 `index.js` 修改补丁直接输出吗？"}],"timestamp":1775911193070}}
{"type":"message","id":"8d6bd5b5","parentId":"df6d6939","timestamp":"2026-04-11T12:40:43.280Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has provided a very detailed implementation plan for Phase 1 and Phase 1.5. They're asking me to learn and provide feedback/thinking first, without immediate operation.\n\nLet me analyze this implementation:\n\n**Phase 1 - Configuration & Validation:**\n- Clear, well-structured JSON files\n- Validation script covers the key checks I mentioned\n- Uses node-cache for classification caching (good)\n\n**Phase 1.5 - External Router Design:**\n- Design principles are sound\n- Implementation location is clear\n- Core routing logic looks reasonable\n- Classifier fallback and caching implemented\n\n**Potential improvements/considerations:**\n\n1. **Security**: The config files contain API keys via env var placeholders - need to ensure `.env` is properly secured\n2. **Error handling**: What happens if the proxy process doesn't have permission to read config files?\n3. **Hot reload**: No mention of config hot reload - might need cron or file watcher\n4. **Logging format**: Should follow the earlier JSON logging spec for observability\n5. **Missing validation**: The validation script doesn't check regex syntax validity in routing rules\n6. **Workspace**: The agent workspace paths need to exist or be created\n\nI should provide my analysis and then wait for the user's confirmation before executing.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## Phase 1 & 1.5 方案学习 & 思考\n\n### 优点\n\n| 点 | 说明 |\n|---|---|\n| 配置完整 | models.json / routing_rules.json 结构清晰，覆盖核心场景 |\n| 校验全面 | 检查了 provider 环境变量、引用一致性、priority 重复 |\n| 设计合理 | 外挂式不修改 Gateway，符合解耦原则 |\n| 缓存内置 | node-cache 做分类器缓存，5分钟 TTL 合理 |\n\n### 需要补充的细节\n\n| 项 | 建议 |\n|---|------|\n| **正则校验** | validation script 中缺少对 routing_rules.json 中 `regex` 字段的语法校验（若后续扩展） |\n| **日志格式** | 建议 router 中使用 Phase 1 方案里定义的 JSON 日志格式，便于后续接入监控 |\n| **目录预创建** | Agent workspace 需要预创建：`/home/ai/.openclaw/agents/{fast,deep}` |\n| **配置热更新** | 可增加 `fs.watch` 监听配置文件变化，自动重载缓存的配置 |\n| **文件权限** | 配置文件应设为 600（`chmod 600 ~/.openclaw/config/*.json`），防止敏感信息泄露 |\n\n### 一个实现细节建议\n\n当前路由逻辑遍历所有 rules 做 priority 排序，适合规则少（<20）的场景。若规则扩展到 50+ 条，可优化为：\n\n```javascript\n// 优化：按 priority 分组，减少遍历\nconst rulesByPriority = {};\nrules.forEach(r => {\n  if (!rulesByPriority[r.priority]) rulesByPriority[r.priority] = [];\n  rulesByPriority[r.priority].push(r);\n});\nconst maxPriority = Math.max(...Object.keys(rulesByPriority).map(Number));\n// 从高 priority 往下匹配，短路更快\n```\n\n---\n\n### 待确认事项\n\n1. **环境变量**：`MINIMAX_API_KEY` 和 `DEEPSEEK_API_KEY` 当前是否已在运行环境中配置？\n2. **Agent workspace**：是否需要我创建 `/home/ai/.openclaw/agents/fast` 和 `deep` 目录？\n\n---\n\n**方案整体可行，暂无需修改。准备好后我可以开始执行 Phase 1。**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":25657,"output":712,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27521,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775911193084,"responseId":"019d7c8e3bc23e7675a1f47cb12c3766"}}
