{"type":"message","id":"90b97fe7","parentId":"90aa4439","timestamp":"2026-04-11T12:50:26.005Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到当前的 openclaw.json 结构。agents 部分比较简单，没有 list 数组。我需要按照方案要求添加 agents.list 配置。\n\n让我看一下原有结构：\n- agents.defaults.model.primary 是 \"volcengine-plan/doubao-seed-2.0-pro\"\n- 没有 agents.list 数组\n\n我需要添加 agents.list 数组，包含 fast_agent 和 deep_agent。\n\n不过有个问题，原有配置使用的是 model 格式（如 \"volcengine-plan/doubao-seed-2.0-pro\"），而方案中使用的是 modelRef 引用 models.json 中的逻辑名称。\n\n这意味着我需要小心合并，确保不破坏现有配置。\n\n让我创建新的 agents 结构：\n- 在 agents 下添加 list 数组\n- 保持 defaults 不变\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e79bf62b77c240e0bb523dc8","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/openclaw.json","edits":[{"oldText":"  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {","newText":"  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"fast_agent\",\n        \"name\": \"Fast Agent\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/home/ai/.openclaw/agents/fast\",\n        \"modelRef\": \"fast\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"deep_agent\",\n        \"name\": \"Deep Agent\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/home/ai/.openclaw/agents/deep\",\n        \"modelRef\": \"deep\"\n      }\n    ],\n    \"defaults\": {"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":32790,"output":346,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33136,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775911820925,"responseId":"chatcmpl-d856d104-d899-4fc4-a8aa-e39fd4477918"}}
