{"type":"message","id":"58a02c3f","parentId":"1ba551ae","timestamp":"2026-04-11T12:50:34.975Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，agents.list 已添加。现在创建环境变量文件 .env 注意用户要求不要实际写真实密钥，所以我创建一个带占位符的文件。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d7c98022f5553a308da012b43032f","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 实际使用时替换为真实密钥\nMINIMAX_API_KEY=your-actual-minimax-key\nDEEPSEEK_API_KEY=your-actual-deepseek-key\nCLASSIFIER_CACHE_TTL=300\nROUTING_LOG_ENABLED=true","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/.env"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":32091,"output":119,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33362,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775911826070,"responseId":"019d7c97ef96800ff0bc346218d4b5dd"}}
