{"type":"message","id":"d11afd5e","parentId":"fe1fd55c","timestamp":"2026-04-11T15:15:57.451Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c83f0c21ccd941ae926784dd","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"...req.body, \n      history,\n      _routing: {\n        targetAgent: routing.agentId,\n        model: modelConfig?.modelId,\n        provider: modelConfig?.provider,\n        by: routing.by\n      }\n    };\n    const gwRes = await axios.post(`${GATEWAY_URL}/api/chat/send`, payload, { timeout: Math.max(scoring.timeout * 1000 + 5000, 30000) });\n    \n    const replyContent = gwRes.data.reply || gwRes.data.content || '';\n    await addContextMessage('assistant', replyContent);\n    \n    // 在返回结果中追加路由信息\n    return res.json({ \n      ...gwRes.data, \n      routing: {\n        targetAgent: routing.agentId,\n        model: modelConfig?.modelId,\n        by: routing.by\n      }\n    });\n  } catch (gwErr) {\n    log('error', 'Gateway forward failed', { error: gwErr.message, status: gwErr.response?.status });\n    return res.status(502).json({ error: `Gateway error: ${gwErr.message}` });\n  }\n  } catch (err) {\n    log('error', 'Proxy error', { error: err.message });\n    try { \n      const gwRes = await axios.post(`${GATEWAY_URL}/api/chat/send`, req.body, { timeout: 30000 });"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":59,"aggregated":"...req.body, \n      history,\n      _routing: {\n        targetAgent: routing.agentId,\n        model: modelConfig?.modelId,\n        provider: modelConfig?.provider,\n        by: routing.by\n      }\n    };\n    const gwRes = await axios.post(`${GATEWAY_URL}/api/chat/send`, payload, { timeout: Math.max(scoring.timeout * 1000 + 5000, 30000) });\n    \n    const replyContent = gwRes.data.reply || gwRes.data.content || '';\n    await addContextMessage('assistant', replyContent);\n    \n    // 在返回结果中追加路由信息\n    return res.json({ \n      ...gwRes.data, \n      routing: {\n        targetAgent: routing.agentId,\n        model: modelConfig?.modelId,\n        by: routing.by\n      }\n    });\n  } catch (gwErr) {\n    log('error', 'Gateway forward failed', { error: gwErr.message, status: gwErr.response?.status });\n    return res.status(502).json({ error: `Gateway error: ${gwErr.message}` });\n  }\n  } catch (err) {\n    log('error', 'Proxy error', { error: err.message });\n    try { \n      const gwRes = await axios.post(`${GATEWAY_URL}/api/chat/send`, req.body, { timeout: 30000 });","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775920557430}}
{"type":"message","id":"cff7ac53","parentId":"d11afd5e","timestamp":"2026-04-11T15:16:34.367Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我理解了完整的现状。让我进行全面思考：\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n### 全面思考总结\n\n**✅ 已完成的工作**：\n\n| 项 | 状态 |\n|---|---|\n| 配置文件创建 | ✅ models.json, routing_rules.json, .env |\n| openclaw.json 更新 | ✅ 添加了 agents.list |\n| 校验脚本 | ✅ validate-config.js |\n| Proxy 路由函数 | ✅ routeAgent, getModelConfig, logRouting |\n| 路由决策逻辑 | ✅ 两阶段：关键词 → 分类器 |\n| 分类器缓存 | ✅ NodeCache 5分钟 TTL |\n| 传递 _routing | ✅ 在 payload 中携带 |\n| 语法修复 | ✅ 刚刚完成 |\n\n**⚠️ 待验证/待完成**：\n\n| 项 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|---|---|---|\n| 路由结果实际生效 | ⚠️ 部分 | 通过 `_routing` 传给了 Gateway，但 **Gateway 还未实现读取和使用** |\n| 模型实际切换 | ❌ 未完成 | 当前只传了参数，Gateway 还是用默认模型 |\n| 测试验证 | ❌ 未做 | 需要重启 proxy 测试 |\n\n---\n\n### 核心问题\n\n**当前只是\"传了路由信息\"**，但 Gateway 没有读取 `_routing` 参数，也没有根据 `model` 选择实际调用的 LLM。\n\n**两种实现路径**：\n\n| 路径 | 说明 | 工作量 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| A: Gateway 读取参数 | Gateway 读取 `_routing.model`，动态选择 LLM | 中等 |\n| B: Agent 映射 | 在 Gateway 中预先配置不同 Agent，Proxy 路由到不同 Agent（id 层面） | 较小 |\n\n---\n\n**建议**：目前配置已就位，但需要 Gateway 配合才能真正实现多模型路由。要继续完成吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":4571,"output":368,"cacheRead":61440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66379,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775920557455,"responseId":"019d7d1d207cfa8bdd953b1ad7593f20"}}
