{"type":"message","id":"115f2d2d","parentId":"0967d555","timestamp":"2026-04-11T15:23:13.121Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-04-11 23:23 GMT+8] 学习，进行思考给出预案，在思考：最优解：Proxy 独立完成路由决策与 LLM 调用，Gateway 仅保留 UI 与 WebSocket 转发。\n\n---\n\n## 一、核心特性\n\n| 特性 | 实现方式 |\n|------|----------|\n| **多模型路由** | 关键词（优先级100）+ 分类器标签（优先级80）→ fallback |\n| **LLM 直调** | 根据 `models.json` 动态选择 API 端点、密钥、模型名 |\n| **故障降级** | 主模型失败时自动切换 `fallback` 模型，支持重试 |\n| **超时控制** | 每个模型配置独立超时，LLM 调用整体超时 60s |\n| **上下文管理** | 从 Context API (3106) 获取历史，调用后存储回复 |\n| **分类器缓存** | NodeCache TTL 5 分钟，减少重复调用 |\n| **Bypass 开关** | 紧急情况下绕过所有智能逻辑，直接转发 Gateway |\n| **结构化日志** | JSON 格式，包含路由决策、模型调用耗时 |\n| **健康检查** | `/health` 返回各依赖状态 |\n| **WebSocket 支持** | 转发 `/ws` 到 Gateway 保持实时通信 |\n\n---\n\n## 二、完整代码\n\n```javascript\nrequire('dotenv').config();\nconst fs = require('fs');\nconst path = require('path');\nconst express = require('express');\nconst http = require('http');\nconst axios = require('axios');\nconst WebSocket = require('ws');\nconst { createProxyMiddleware } = require('http-proxy-middleware');\nconst NodeCache = require('node-cache');\nconst { classify, score } = require('./clients/v8Client');\n\n// ==================== 配置加载 ====================\nconst HOME = process.env.HOME || '/home/ai';\nconst MODELS_CONFIG = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(path.join(HOME, '.openclaw/config/models.json')));\nconst RULES_CONFIG = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(path.join(HOME, '.openclaw/config/routing_rules.json')));\nconst OPENCLAW_CONFIG = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(path.join(HOME, '.openclaw/openclaw.json')));\n\nconst classifyCache = new NodeCache({ stdTTL: parseInt(process.env.CLASSIFIER_CACHE_TTL) || 300 });\n\n// ==================== 日志工具 ====================\nconst log = (level, msg, data = {}) => {\n console.log(JSON.stringify({\n level,\n ts: new Date().toISOString(),\n msg,\n ...data\n }));\n};\n\n// ==================== 路由决策 ====================\nfunction getModelConfig(agentId) {\n const agent = (OPENCLAW_CONFIG.agents?.list || []).find(a => a.id === agentId);\n const modelRef = agent?.modelRef || 'fast';\n const modelConfig = MODELS_CONFIG.models[modelRef];\n if (!modelConfig) throw new Error(`Model ref '${modelRef}' not found in models.json`);\n const provider = MODELS_CONFIG.providers[modelConfig.provider];\n if (!provider) throw new Error(`Provider '${modelConfig.provider}' not found`);\n return { modelRef, modelConfig, provider };\n}\n\nfunction routeAgent(userMessage, classifierResult = null) {\n const rules = [...RULES_CONFIG.rules].sort((a, b) => b.priority - a.priority);\n \n // 阶段1：关键词（优先级 ≥ 100）\n for (const rule of rules) {\n if (rule.priority < 100) continue;\n if (rule.condition.always) continue;\n if (rule.condition.contains) {\n const matched = rule.condition.contains.some(kw => userMessage.includes(kw));\n if (matched) {\n const { modelConfig } = getModelConfig(rule.target_agent);\n log('info', 'Route by keyword', { rule: rule.id, agent: rule.target_agent, model: modelConfig.modelId });\n return { agentId: rule.target_agent, by: 'keyword' };\n }\n }\n }\n \n // 阶段2：分类器标签\n if (classifierResult) {\n for (const rule of rules) {\n if (rule.condition.always) continue;\n if (!rule.condition.classifier_label) continue;\n const matched = rule.condition.classifier_label.includes(classifierResult.scene);\n if (matched) {\n const { modelConfig } = getModelConfig(rule.target_agent);\n log('info', 'Route by classifier', { rule: rule.id, agent: rule.target_agent, model: modelConfig.modelId });\n return { agentId: rule.target_agent, by: 'classifier' };\n }\n }\n }\n \n // Fallback\n const fallback = rules.find(r => r.condition.always);\n const target = fallback ? fallback.target_agent : 'fast_agent';\n const { modelConfig } = getModelConfig(target);\n log('info', 'Route fallback', { agent: target, model: modelConfig.modelId });\n return { agentId: target, by: 'fallback' };\n}\n\n// ==================== LLM 调用（支持降级重试） ====================\nasync function callLLMWithRetry(provider, modelConfig, messages, retries = 0) {\n const url = `${provider.baseUrl}/chat/completions`;\n const headers = {\n 'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n 'Authorization': `Bearer ${provider.apiKey}`\n };\n const payload = {\n model: modelConfig.modelId,\n messages,\n temperature: 0.7,\n max_tokens: 4096\n };\n \n try {\n const response = await axios.post(url, payload, {\n headers,\n timeout: modelConfig.timeout || 60000\n });\n return response.data.choices[0].message.content;\n } catch (err) {\n log('warn', 'LLM call failed', { model: modelConfig.modelId, error: err.message, retry: retries });\n if (retries < (modelConfig.maxRetries || 1)) {\n await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 1000 * (retries + 1)));\n return callLLMWithRetry(provider, modelConfig, messages, retries + 1);\n }\n // 尝试 fallback\n if (modelConfig.fallback) {\n const fallbackModel = MODELS_CONFIG.models[modelConfig.fallback];\n if (fallbackModel) {\n const fallbackProvider = MODELS_CONFIG.providers[fallbackModel.provider];\n log('info', 'Falling back to model', { fallback: modelConfig.fallback });\n return callLLMWithRetry(fallbackProvider, fallbackModel, messages, 0);\n }\n }\n throw err;\n }\n}\n\n// ==================== 上下文 API 辅助 ====================\nconst CONTEXT_API = process.env.CONTEXT_API || 'http://localhost:3106';\nasync function getContextHistory() {\n try {\n const res = await axios.get(`${CONTEXT_API}/api/context/full`, { timeout: 2000 });\n return res.data.messages || [];\n } catch { return []; }\n}\nasync function addContextMessage(role, content) {\n try {\n await axios.post(`${CONTEXT_API}/api/context`, { role, content }, { timeout: 2000 });\n } catch (e) { log('warn', 'Context add failed', { error: e.message }); }\n}\n\n// ==================== 任务提交 ====================\nconst V8_TASK_API = process.env.V8_TASK_API || 'http://localhost:3103/api/task';\nasync function submitV8Task(message, scoring) {\n const payload = {\n type: 'command',\n command: message.trim().split(/\\s+/)[0] || 'echo',\n args: message.trim().split(/\\s+/).slice(1),\n timeout: scoring.timeout,\n priority: Math.floor(scoring.score / 20),\n metadata: { prompt: message, strategy: scoring.recommendedStrategy }\n };\n const res = await axios.post(V8_TASK_API, payload, { timeout: 5000 });\n return res.data.id;\n}\n\n// ==================== Express App ====================\nconst app = express();\napp.use(express.json());\napp.use(express.static(path.join(__dirname, 'public')));\n\nconst PORT = process.env.PROXY_PORT || 3102;\nconst GATEWAY_URL = process.env.GATEWAY_URL || 'http://localhost:3108';\nconst GATEWAY_WS = process.env.GATEWAY_WS || 'ws://localhost:3108';\nconst BYPASS_MODE = process.env.BYPASS_MODE === 'true';\nlet bypass = BYPASS_MODE;\n\napp.get('/health', async (req, res) => {\n const status = { proxy: 'ok', bypass };\n try { await axios.get(`${process.env.CLASSIFIER_URL || 'http://localhost:3104'}/health`, { timeout: 1000 }); status.classifier = 'ok'; } catch { status.classifier = 'down'; }\n try { await axios.get('http://localhost:3103/health', { timeout: 1000 }); status.v8 = 'ok'; } catch { status.v8 = 'down'; }\n try { await axios.get(`${CONTEXT_API}/health`, { timeout: 1000 }); status.context = 'ok'; } catch { status.context = 'down'; }\n res.json(status);\n});\n\napp.post('/admin/bypass', (req, res) => {\n bypass = req.body.enabled === true;\n log('info', 'Bypass toggled', { bypass });\n res.json({ bypass });\n});\n\n// ==================== 核心消息处理 ====================\napp.post('/api/chat/send', async (req, res) => {\n const { message, context = {} } = req.body;\n if (!message) return res.status(400).json({ error: 'message required' });\n\n await addContextMessage('user', message);\n\n // Bypass 模式：直接转发 Gateway\n if (bypass) {\n try {\n const gwRes = await axios.post(`${GATEWAY_URL}/api/chat/send`, req.body, { timeout: 60000 });\n await addContextMessage('assistant', gwRes.data.reply || '');\n return res.json(gwRes.data);\n } catch (err) {\n return res.status(502).json({ error: 'Gateway unavailable in bypass mode' });\n }\n }\n\n try {\n // 1. 获取分类结果（带缓存）\n let classifierResult = classifyCache.get(message);\n if (!classifierResult) {\n try {\n classifierResult = await classify(message);\n classifyCache.set(message, classifierResult);\n } catch (e) {\n log('warn', 'Classifier unavailable, using keyword fallback', { error: e.message });\n classifierResult = null;\n }\n }\n\n // 2. 路由决策\n const routing = routeAgent(message, classifierResult);\n const { modelConfig, provider } = getModelConfig(routing.agentId);\n log('info', 'Routed', { agent: routing.agentId, model: modelConfig.modelId, by: routing.by });\n\n // 3. 非任务快速回复\n if (classifierResult && !classifierResult.isTask) {\n const replies = {\n chitchat: '你好！有什么技术问题需要帮助？',\n fault_recovery: '请描述具体的故障现象和已尝试的操作，我将协助恢复。',\n vague_request: '我不太确定你的具体需求。请具体说明。'\n };\n const reply = replies[classifierResult.scene] || '收到消息。';\n await addContextMessage('assistant', reply);\n return res.json({ reply, scene: classifierResult.scene, agent: routing.agentId });\n }\n\n // 4. 任务评分\n const scoring = await score(message, context);\n log('info', 'Scored', { score: scoring.score, strategy: scoring.recommendedStrategy });\n\n // 5. 策略路由\n if (scoring.recommendedStrategy === 'DIRECT') {\n const taskId = await submitV8Task(message, scoring);\n const reply = `✅ 任务已提交 (ID: ${taskId})，预计 ${scoring.timeout}s 完成。`;\n await addContextMessage('assistant', reply);\n return res.json({ reply, taskId, strategy: 'DIRECT', agent: routing.agentId });\n }\n\n // 6. 非 DIRECT 任务：由 Proxy 直接调用 LLM\n const history = await getContextHistory();\n const messages = [\n ...history,\n { role: 'user', content: message }\n ];\n \n const llmReply = await callLLMWithRetry(provider, modelConfig, messages);\n await addContextMessage('assistant', llmReply);\n \n res.json({\n reply: llmReply,\n agent: routing.agentId,\n model: modelConfig.modelId,\n strategy: scoring.recommendedStrategy\n });\n\n } catch (err) {\n log('error', 'Processing failed', { error: err.message, stack: err.stack });\n // 终极兜底：转发给 Gateway\n try {\n const gwRes = await axios.post(`${GATEWAY_URL}/api/chat/send`, req.body, { timeout: 60000 });\n await addContextMessage('assistant', gwRes.data.reply || '');\n return res.json({ ...gwRes.data, fallback: true });\n } catch {\n return res.status(502).json({ error: 'All services unavailable' });\n }\n }\n});\n\n// ==================== 转发非 API 请求与 WebSocket ====================\nconst server = http.createServer(app);\nconst gatewayProxy = createProxyMiddleware({\n target: GATEWAY_URL,\n changeOrigin: true,\n ws: true,\n logLevel: 'silent',\n onError: (err, req, res) => {\n log('error', 'Gateway proxy error', { error: err.message });\n if (res && !res.headersSent) res.status(502).send('Gateway unavailable');\n }\n});\n\napp.use('/', gatewayProxy);\n\nserver.on('upgrade', (req, socket, head) => {\n log('info', 'WebSocket upgrade', { url: req.url });\n gatewayProxy.upgrade(req, socket, head);\n});\n\nserver.listen(PORT, () => {\n log('info', `Proxy started on ${PORT}`, { gateway: GATEWAY_URL });\n});\n\nprocess.on('SIGTERM', () => process.exit(0));\nprocess.on('SIGINT', () => process.exit(0));\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、部署验证\n\n### 1. 依赖检查\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/proxy\nnpm list node-cache || npm install node-cache\n```\n\n### 2. 重启代理\n```bash\nsystemctl --user restart openclaw-proxy\n# 或 pm2 restart openclaw-proxy\n```\n\n### 3. 测试\n```bash\n# 闲聊（应快速回复模板）\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3102/api/chat/send -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"message\":\"你好\"}'\n\n# 编程任务（应调用 MiniMax 模型并返回结果）\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3102/api/chat/send -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"message\":\"用Python写一个斐波那契函数\"}'\n```\n\n观察日志确认路由决策与模型调用：\n```bash\njournalctl --user -u openclaw-proxy -f | grep -E \"Routed|LLM\"\n```\n\n---"}],"timestamp":1775920993110}}
{"type":"message","id":"0046cd1f","parentId":"115f2d2d","timestamp":"2026-04-11T15:23:58.249Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户给我提供了一个更完整的方案，这是**最优解**：Proxy 独立完成路由决策与 LLM 调用，Gateway 仅保留 UI 与 WebSocket 转发。\n\n这和之前的方案不同点在于：\n- 之前：Proxy 只是路由，然后把请求转发给 Gateway，让 Gateway 决定用哪个模型\n- 现在：Proxy 直接根据路由结果调用对应的 LLM API，不再依赖 Gateway 的模型选择\n\n这是一个更彻底的解耦方案。\n\n让我思考一下这个方案的关键点：\n\n1. **配置加载**：从 models.json, routing_rules.json, openclaw.json 加载配置\n2. **路由决策**：关键词 + 分类器标签 → 确定 target_agent\n3. **模型获取**：根据 target_agent → modelRef → 从 models.json 获取实际模型配置\n4. **LLM 调用**：callLLMWithRetry 函数根据 provider 配置直接调用对应 API\n5. **故障降级**：主模型失败时自动切换 fallback 模型\n6. **上下文管理**：从 Context API 获取历史消息\n\n优势：\n- Gateway 完全不需要改动\n- Proxy 完全掌控路由和模型选择\n- 职责清晰，耦合度低\n\n需要做的事情：\n1. 用新的完整代码替换当前的 proxy/index.js\n\n\n2. 确保 node-cache 已安装\n3. 重启并测试\n\n让我给出思考总结。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n### 方案学习与思考\n\n**核心变化**：从\"Proxy 路由 → Gateway 调用 LLM\" 变为 \"**Proxy 直接调用 LLM**\"\n\n| 对比项 | 之前方案 | 最优解方案 |\n|--------|----------|-----------|\n| LLM 调用 | Gateway 负责 | Proxy 直接调用 |\n| 模型选择 | Gateway 读取参数 | Proxy 根据 agentId → modelRef 直接选择 |\n| Gateway 改动 | 需要 | 不需要 |\n| 耦合度 | 中（需两端配合） | 低（Proxy 全责） |\n\n---\n\n### 实现要点\n\n| 功能 | 实现位置 |\n|------|----------|\n| 路由决策 | `routeAgent()` - 关键词 + 分类器标签 |\n| 模型解析 | `getModelConfig(agentId)` - agentId → modelRef → model |\n| LLM 调用 | `callLLMWithRetry()` - 直接调用 provider API，支持 fallback |\n| 上下文 | `getContextHistory()` / `addContextMessage()` |\n\n---\n\n### 需要执行的操作\n\n1. **用新代码完全替换** `~/.openclaw/proxy/index.js`\n2. **检查依赖** `node-cache` 已安装\n3. **重启测试**\n\n---\n\n**这个方案更简洁明确。要我直接用这个完整代码替换当前的 index.js 吗？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":5122,"output":536,"cacheRead":64512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70170,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775920993135,"responseId":"019d7d23c66442702c5a1134122934de"}}
