{"type":"message","id":"e1521a84","parentId":"35209ce4","timestamp":"2026-04-11T18:26:23.241Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我总结完成了方案的哪些内容。让我回顾一下这次任务中完成的工作。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n### 已完成内容\n\n| 项 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|---|---|---|\n| **配置文件** | ✅ | models.json, routing_rules.json, providers.json |\n| **Agent 定义** | ✅ | openclaw.json 中添加 agents.list 含 modelRef |\n| **校验脚本** | ✅ | validate-config.js |\n| **ai-router 安装** | ✅ | npm install @isaced/ai-router |\n| **Proxy 代码** | ✅ | 重写 index.js 集成 ai-router |\n| **分类服务** | ✅ | 3104 正常工作 |\n| **V8 评分** | ✅ | 3103 正常运行 |\n\n---\n\n### 未完成\n\n| 项 | 状态 |\n|---|---|\n| **Proxy 启动** | ❌ 因依赖问题未能成功运行 |\n| **端到端测试** | ❌ 需要修复启动问题后测试 |\n\n---\n\n**需要修复的问题**：Proxy 从 `~/.openclaw/proxy/index.js` 复制到 `~/openclaw-router/openclaw-router.js` 后因缺少 node_modules 依赖而无法启动。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":90069,"output":237,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90306,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775931979057,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b534d5bd-9cd4-40ba-b947-cc24c47fd0e6"}}
