{"type":"message","id":"2b54bdeb","parentId":"de1bb0fe","timestamp":"2026-04-11T18:27:51.683Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在让我全局思考整个方案的状态，不要操作。让我思考一下当前的整体情况和下一步应该怎么做。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n### 全局思考\n\n**现状**：\n- 核心代码已完成（配置 + Proxy 逻辑）\n- 依赖服务正常（3103 V8, 3104 Classifier）\n- 唯一卡点：**Proxy 无法启动**（缺少 node_modules）\n\n**问题根源**：\n```\n~/.openclaw/proxy/     → 有 node_modules（含 ai-router）\n~/openclaw-router/     → 无 node_modules（新代码复制过去后缺依赖）\n```\n\n**两个解决思路**：\n\n| 方案 | 操作 | 复杂度 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| **A**: 在 ~/openclaw-router/ 安装依赖 | cd 过去 npm install | 简单 |\n| **B**: 修改 systemd 服务指向 ~/.openclaw/proxy/ | 改 ExecStart 路径 | 需要验证 |\n\n**建议方案 A**，因为：\n- 不改变现有服务结构\n- 快速解决\n- 后续可考虑统一目录\n\n---\n\n**需要我执行方案 A 吗？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":90350,"output":221,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90571,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775932067637,"responseId":"chatcmpl-7b6d5c53-eea0-47c7-a263-a71890715585"}}
