{"type":"message","id":"be8107cf","parentId":"245eb615","timestamp":"2026-04-11T18:29:55.724Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_753cd7b6501a4a378d200df8","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"name\": \"@isaced/ai-router\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.2\",\n  \"description\": \"A lightweight, framework-agnostic router for AI/LLM API requests.\",\n  \"main\": \"src/index.ts\",\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"exports\": \"./src/index.ts\",\n  \"keywords\": [\n    \"ai\",\n    \"llm\",\n    \"router\",\n    \"api\",\n    \"request\"\n  ],\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"test\": \"bun test\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@types/bun\": \"^1.2.19\"\n  },\n  \"repository\": {\n    \"type\": \"git\",\n    \"url\": \"git+https://github.com/isaced/ai-router.git\"\n  },\n  \"homepage\": \"https://github.com/isaced/ai-router\",\n  \"author\": \"isaced\",\n  \"license\": \"MIT\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":42,"aggregated":"{\n  \"name\": \"@isaced/ai-router\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.2\",\n  \"description\": \"A lightweight, framework-agnostic router for AI/LLM API requests.\",\n  \"main\": \"src/index.ts\",\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"exports\": \"./src/index.ts\",\n  \"keywords\": [\n    \"ai\",\n    \"llm\",\n    \"router\",\n    \"api\",\n    \"request\"\n  ],\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"test\": \"bun test\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@types/bun\": \"^1.2.19\"\n  },\n  \"repository\": {\n    \"type\": \"git\",\n    \"url\": \"git+https://github.com/isaced/ai-router.git\"\n  },\n  \"homepage\": \"https://github.com/isaced/ai-router\",\n  \"author\": \"isaced\",\n  \"license\": \"MIT\"\n}","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775932195714}}
{"type":"message","id":"945b5fcc","parentId":"be8107cf","timestamp":"2026-04-11T18:30:14.636Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"AH! This is a **major problem**!\n\nThe package uses:\n- `\"type\": \"module\"` - ES modules\n- `\"main\": \"src/index.ts\"` - TypeScript source\n\nNode.js cannot directly import `.ts` files or ES modules without configuration. This is why the proxy is failing!\n\nThis is a critical bug in my code. I used CommonJS require() to import an ES module package.\n\nLet me verify this is the issue, and consider the solutions:\n1. Use dynamic import() instead of require\n2. Transpile the package\n3. Find an alternative package that supports CommonJS\n\nLet me present this finding to the user.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n### ⚠️ 关键问题发现\n\n| 问题 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **ai-router 是 ES Module** | 包使用 `\"type\": \"module\"` 且导出 TypeScript 源文件 |\n| **代码使用 CommonJS** | `require('@isaced/ai-router')` 无法加载 ES Module |\n\n**这就是启动失败的真正原因！**\n\n---\n\n### 解决方案\n\n| 方案 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **A**: 改用 `import()` 动态导入 | 需要将代码改为 async 方式 |\n| **B**: 使用 esm 库转换 | 需要额外依赖 |\n| **C**: 替换为 CommonJS 兼容的路由库 | 需要找替代品 |\n\n---\n\n**建议方案 A**（最小改动），需要修改代码开头：\n\n```javascript\n// 改前\nconst { AIRouter } = require('@isaced/ai-router');\n\n// 改后\nconst { AIRouter } = await import('@isaced/ai-router');\n```\n\n但这需要整个启动流程改为 async，比较复杂。\n\n**另一个思路**：用旧版 proxy 代码（不集成 ai-router），先让服务跑起来。\n\n要怎么处理？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":738,"output":376,"cacheRead":94464,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95578,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775932195727,"responseId":"019d7dcdfa395a0382f4ec66627a1127"}}
