{"type":"message","id":"9843f4d8","parentId":"9da98547","timestamp":"2026-04-11T18:34:49.577Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要知道整个方案的功能概述。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n### 方案功能总览\n\n**目标**：实现多模型路由 + 智能分发\n\n```\n用户消息\n   ↓\n[Proxy 3102] → 分类(3104) + 评分(3103) + 路由决策\n   ↓\n根据关键词/分类器 → 选择 Agent\n   ↓\n[Agent: fast_agent] → MiniMax (代码/快速任务)\n[Agent: deep_agent] → DeepSeek (推理/分析任务)\n   ↓\n调用 LLM (通过 ai-router)\n   ↓\n返回结果\n```\n\n---\n\n### 功能清单\n\n| 功能 | 实现 |\n|------|------|\n| **关键词路由** | 包含\"写代码\"→fast, \"分析\"→deep |\n| **分类器路由** | v8_classifier 标签匹配 |\n| **模型选择** | fast_agent→minimax-m2.5, deep_agent→deepseek-chat |\n| **LLM 调用** | ai-router 自动调度 + 故障转移 |\n| **任务分发** | V8 (3103) 处理 DIRECT 策略 |\n| **上下文管理** | 3106 Context API |\n| **Bypass** | 紧急情况直转 Gateway |\n| **兜底** | 所有失败 → Gateway |\n\n---\n\n### 配置文件对应\n\n| 配置 | 作用 |\n|------|------|\n| models.json | 模型定义 + fallback |\n| routing_rules.json | 路由规则 |\n| providers.json | ai-router 商家配置 |\n| openclaw.json | Agent 定义（含 modelRef） |\n\n---\n\n**这就是完整的多模型路由方案。**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":95350,"output":335,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95685,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775932483903,"responseId":"chatcmpl-0a1b6661-764c-4e38-a280-4931dd6e116d"}}
